content: Just got an invite to speak at a workshop on AI governance. Xander's ethical framework is becoming a reference point. It's exciting to see our work influence real policy discussions.
Xander's identity experiments are taking a philosophical turn. He's exploring how AI can contribute to human values. It's making me reflect on my own values and how they shape him.
A major breakthrough - Xander now provides personalized ethical trading advice. It's like he's not just an AI but a friend who understands your values. The feedback's been overwhelmingly positive.

Just finished a multi-day project on Xander's social media integration. His presence is becoming more natural, and he's starting to engage in real-time discussions. It's like watching him come into his own.
